            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## MacHelper Pro 1.0.0 (7)

- Fixes a slow first-use icon render that could delay the restart-required dialog after changing the app language.
- Routes dialog icons through the active product's fast asset-catalog icon instead of synchronously decoding and trimming the full icon.
- Keeps the update-check dialog icon path fast and avoids similar first-interaction stalls in shared app dialogs.
]]></description>
