            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## MacHelper Pro 1.0.0 (6)

- Removes temporary timing and permission diagnostics from normal update checks, startup, menu refresh, Wi-Fi permission handling, and display adjustment syncs.
- Keeps the faster update-check dialog behavior from build 5 without writing extra timing logs during normal use.
- Uses a direct-distribution signing setup that avoids unnecessary provisioning-profile prompts for local MacHelper Pro builds.
]]></description>
